quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  43,57,"“Ndipo pamene lidaperekedwa fanizo la mwana wa Mariya, pamenepo anthu anu adali kufuula (monyoza)"
  43,58,"“Ndipo adati: “Kodi milungu yathu ndi yabwino, kapena iye?” Sadamfanizire kwa iwe koma kufuna kutsutsana basi (kopanda kufuna choona). Koma iwo ndi anthu amtsutso"
  43,59,“Iye sadali kanthu koma ndi kapolo amene tidampatsa mtendere; ndipo tidamchita kukhala chitsanzo (chodabwitsa) cha ana a Israyeli
  43,60,“Ndipo tikadafuna tikadawachita angelo kukhala pa dziko mmalo mwa inu ndi kumasiirana iwo kwa iwo (kuti mudziwe kuti angelo akugonjera malamulo a Allah. Iwo siAllah)
  43,61,"“Ndipo iye (Isa (Yesu) adzakhala chizindikiro cha Qiyâma (kuti yayandikira). Choncho musaikaikire, koma nditsatireni. Imeneyi ndi njira yolunjika"
  43,62,“Asakutsekerezeni satana; iye kwa inu ndi mdani woonekera
  43,63,"“Ndipo pamene Isa (Yesu) adadza ndi zisonyezo zoonekera poyera, adati: “Ndakudzerani ndi nzeru (yopindulitsa), ndikuti ndikulongosolereni zina zimene mudali kusiyana mu izo; choncho, muopeni Allah ndiponso ndimvereni.”"
  43,64,““Ndithu Allah ndiye Mbuye wanga ndi Mbuye wanunso; choncho mupembedzeni; imeneyi ndiyo njira yolunjika.”
  43,65,“Koma magulu adasemphana pakati pawo. Ndipo kuonongeka kuchokera mu chilango cha tsiku lowawa kudzakhala pa amene adzichitira okha zoipa
  43,66,"“Palibe chimene akuyembekeza, koma Qiyâma basi yomwe iwadzera mwadzidzidzi pomwe iwo sakuzindikira (ali otanganidwa ndi za m’dziko)"
  43,67,"“Abwenzi tsiku limenelo adzakhala odana, wina ndi mnzake, (chifukwa chakuti adali kuthandizana pa zinthu zosalungama ndi zamachimo) kupatula oopa Allah (amene adachita chibwenzi mwa Allah, pothandizana kukwaniritsa malamulo a Allah ndi kusiya zimene Allah waletsa)"
  43,68,"“(Allah adzati): E inu akapolo Anga (abwino)! Palibe kuopa kwa inu lerolino ndiponso simudandaula"
  43,69,“Amene adakhulupirira zisonyezo Zathu ndipo adali Asilamu (ogonjera Allah)
  43,70,"“Lowani ku Munda wamtendere, inu ndi akazi anu musangalatsidwa"
  43,71,"“Adzakhala akupititsidwa mbale zagolide ndi matambula (agolide); zonse zokomera moyo zidzakhala mmenemo ndi zokomera maso, ndipo inu mudzakhala mmenemo nthawi yaitali"
  43,72,“Ndipo umeneo ndi munda umene mwapatsidwa chifukwa cha (zabwino) zimene munkachita
  43,73,“Inu mupeza mmenemo zipatso zambiri zomwe muzidya
  43,74,“Ndithu ochimwa (okanira) adzakhala m’chilango cha Jahannam nthawi yaitali
  43,75,"“Sadzapatsidwa nthawi yopumula, ndipo mmenemo iwo akataya mtima (zakupeza moyo wabwino)"
  43,76,“Ndipo sitidawapondereze koma adali kudzipondereza okha
  43,77,"“Ndipo (okanira) adzaitana E iwe Malik! (yemwe ndi mngelo woyang’anira moto): ‘‘Mbuye wako atipatse imfa (kuti tipumule kuchilangochi!)” Adzanena (Malik): “Ndithu inu mukhala momwemo!”"
  43,78,“Ndithu tidakubweretserani choona; koma ambiri a inu mudali kuchida choona
  43,79,"“Kodi akonza bwino chikonzero (chawocho chomwe ndi chiwembu chofuna kumupha Mtumiki {s.a.w})? Ndithu nafenso ndife okonza chikonzero chabwino (cholepheretsa chiwembu chawocho)"
  43,80,"“Kodi akuganiza kuti sitikumva zobisa zawo ndi zonong’oneza zawo? Iyayi, (tikuzimva zonse), ndipo atumiki Athu (angelo) ali nawo pamodzi; akulemba"
  43,81,"“Nena (kwa omphatikiza Allah ndi mafano): “Zikadakhala kuti (Allah) Wachifundo chambiri ali ndi mwana, ndiye kuti ine ndikadakhala woyamba kumpembedza (mwanayo).”"
  43,82,"“Mbuye wa kumwamba ndi pansi, Mbuye wa Arsh (Mpando wachifumu), Wapatukana ndi mbiri zimene akum’nenerazo (zoti Allah ali ndi mwana)"
  43,83,“Asiye azingonena zachabezo ndi kusewera kufikira adzakumana ndi tsiku lawo limene akulonjezedwa
  43,84,"“Ndipo Iye ndiamene akupembedzedwa kumwamba, ndiponso ndi Iye Amene akupembedzedwa pansi. Iye ndi Wanzeru zakuya, Wodziwa kwambiri"
  43,85,“Ndipo watukuka kwambiri Yemwe ufumu wa kumwamba ndi pansi ndi pakati pa zimenezi ndi Wake. Ndiponso kwa Iye ndiko kuli kudziwa kudza kwa tsiku la Qiyâma; ndipo kwa Iye Yekha ndi kumene m’dzabwezedwa
  43,86,"“Ndipo omwe akuwapembedzawo kusiya Iye (Allah), sangathe kupulumutsa (aliyense) kupatula amene akuikira umboni choonachi, pomwe iwo akuchidziwa bwino"
  43,87,"“Ndipo ngati utawafunsa: “Ndani adawalenga?” Anena motsimikiza kuti: “Ndi Allah.” Nanga akutembenuzidwa bwanji (kusiya choona)"
  43,88,"“Ndipo zonena zake (Mneneri Muhammad{s.a.w} nthawi zonse): “E Mbuye Wanga! Ndithu awa ndi anthu osakhulupirira (nditani nao)?”"
  43,89,"“Choncho, akhululukire, ndipo auze mawu a mtendere. Posachedwa adzadziwa"
  44,1,“Hâ-Mîm
  44,2,“Ndikulumbilira buku lofotokoza momveka
  44,3,“Ndithu tidaivumbulutsa (Qur’an) mu usiku wodala. Ife ndithu Ndiachenjezi
  44,4,“Mu (usiku) umenewu chinthu chilichonse chanzeru chimaweruzidwa ndi kulongosoledwa
  44,5,“Mwa chilamulo chochokera kwa Ife. Ndithu Ife ndife otumiza atumiki (kuti achenjeze anthu)
  44,6,"“(Chifukwa cha) chifundo chochokera kwa Mbuye wako. Ndithu Iye Ngwakumva zonse, Wodziwa kwabasi"
  44,7,"“Mbuye wa thambo ndi nthaka ndi zapakati pake, ngati muli otsimikiza"
  44,8,"“Palibe wopembedzedwa moona koma Iye basi. Amapereka moyo ndikupereka imfa, Mbuye wanu ndi Mbuye wa makolo anu oyamba"
  44,9,"“Koma iwo (okanira) ali mchikaiko akungosewera, (potsatira zilakolako zawo zoipa)"
  44,10,"“Basi, yembekezera tsiku limene thambo lidzadze ndi utsi woonekera (konsekonse)"
  44,11,"“Udzawaphimba anthu onse (ndipo adzakhala akunena:) “Ichi ndi chilango chowawa"
  44,12,"“E Mbuye wathu! Tichotsereni chilangochi, ndithu ife tikhulupirira.”"
  44,13,“(Kodi lero) kukumbukira kuwapindulira chiyani iwo? Chikhalirecho mtumiki wolongosola chilichonse adawadzera
  44,14,"“Koma sadamlabadire uku akumnena kuti: “Waphunzitsidwa (ndi anthu), ndiponso wopenga.”"
  44,15,“Ndithu Ife tichotsa chilangocho pang’ono (koma) inu mubwerezanso (machimo anu)
  44,16,"“(Kumbuka, iwe Mtumiki), tsiku limene tidzawalanga chilango chachikulu; ndithu Ife ndife olanga"